Conclusion
Summary of the Project:
Our goal at the Pet Adoption Portal is to help create a pet adoption online platform by using an intelligent, user-friendly design that can continuously evolve. It will make us search for pets easier as it simplifies by the provision of real information and so centralizing adoption process
Anticipated Results and Benefits;
Ultimately, the project intends to allow more people in Michigan easier access to prospective adoptable pets. This, in turn further elevates the productivity of some rescue shelters and breeders as they are given a platform to manage pet listings & adoptions. Ultimately, the Pet Adoption Portal will help more pets find loving homes.
